<h1>Expressive Fonts Pack</h1>
<p class="lead">Color and morphology fonts for hero sections, marketing, and creative contexts. Not appropriate for body text.</p>

<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr><th>Type</th><td>Font pack (theme tokens + effect helpers)</td></tr>
    <tr><th>Theme CSS</th><td><code>packs/fonts-expressive.theme.css</code></td></tr>
    <tr><th>Total weight</th><td>~610KB (3 woff2 files)</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<section>
  <h2>Fonts Included</h2>

  <h3>Nabla &mdash; COLR v1 Color Font</h3>
  <p>A color font using the COLR v1 format &mdash; the browser composites multiple color layers natively. Axes: <code>EDPT</code> (0&ndash;200, extrusion depth) and <code>FLAT</code> (0&ndash;100, flattens perspective). The <code>EDPT</code> axis is animatable with <code>@property</code>, creating a depth-breathing effect. Assigns to <code>--vb-font-nabla</code>.</p>

  <aside style="padding: var(--size-s) var(--size-m); background: var(--color-surface-alt); border-radius: var(--radius-m); border-inline-start: 4px solid var(--color-accent, var(--color-primary)); margin-block: var(--size-m);">
    <strong>Browser support:</strong> COLR v1 requires Chrome 98+, Firefox 107+, Safari 17.2+. Below these versions, Nabla renders as a flat black outline. Gated behind <code>@supports (font-palette: normal)</code>.
  </aside>

  <h3>Honk &mdash; Inflatable Neon</h3>
  <p>Rounded, inflatable morphology font. Axes: <code>MORF</code> (&minus;40&ndash;40) and <code>SHLN</code> (0&ndash;50, shine). Assigns to <code>--vb-font-honk</code>.</p>

  <h3>Kablammo &mdash; Comic Impact</h3>
  <p>High-energy comic-style display font. Axis: <code>MORF</code> (&minus;40&ndash;40). Assigns to <code>--vb-font-kablammo</code>.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Loading</h2>

{% set linkCode %}<link rel="stylesheet" href="/cdn/packs/fonts-expressive.theme.css">{% endset %}

  <code-block language="html" label="Via link tag">{{ linkCode | escape }}</code-block>

{% set jsCode %}import { activateBundle } from 'vanilla-breeze';
await activateBundle('fonts-expressive');{% endset %}

  <code-block language="js" label="Via JS">{{ jsCode | escape }}</code-block>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Usage</h2>

{% set nablaCode %}<p class="vb-nabla" data-effect="depth-pulse">HELLO</p>{% endset %}

  <code-block language="html" label="Nabla with depth pulse">{{ nablaCode | escape }}</code-block>

{% set cssUsage %}.hero-title {
  font-family: var(--vb-font-nabla);
  font-variation-settings: 'EDPT' var(--vb-nabla-depth), 'FLAT' 0;
}
.accent-text {
  font-family: var(--vb-font-honk);
  font-variation-settings: 'MORF' var(--vb-honk-morf);
}{% endset %}

  <code-block language="css" label="Direct usage via tokens">{{ cssUsage | escape }}</code-block>
</section>

